{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":625,"text":"I love my food."},{"time":2375,"text":"And I love information."},{"time":5181,"text":"My children usually tell me"},{"time":8496,"text":"that one of those passions is a little more apparent than the other."},{"time":11958,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14042,"text":"But what I want to do in the next eight minutes or so"},{"time":16292,"text":"is to take you through how those passions developed,"},{"time":18500,"text":"the point in my life when the two passions merged,"},{"time":21860,"text":"the journey of learning that took place from that point."},{"time":26825,"text":"And one idea I want to leave you with today"},{"time":29621,"text":"is what would would happen differently in your life"},{"time":32227,"text":"if you saw information the way you saw food?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36869,"text":"I was born in Calcutta --"},{"time":39040,"text":"a family where my father and his father before him"},{"time":42875,"text":"were journalists,"},{"time":44602,"text":"and they wrote magazines in the English language."},{"time":47625,"text":"That was the family business."},{"time":49833,"text":"And as a result of that,"},{"time":51583,"text":"I grew up with books everywhere around the house."},{"time":54542,"text":"And I mean books everywhere around the house."},{"time":57987,"text":"And that's actually a shop in Calcutta,"},{"time":60458,"text":"but it's a place where we like our books."},{"time":63960,"text":"In fact, I've got 38,000 of them now"},{"time":67262,"text":"and no Kindle in sight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69740,"text":"But growing up as a child with the books around everywhere,"},{"time":75155,"text":"with people to talk to about those books,"},{"time":77677,"text":"this wasn't a sort of slightly learned thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80748,"text":"By the time I was 18, I had a deep passion for books."},{"time":84258,"text":"It wasn't the only passion I had."},{"time":86779,"text":"I was a South Indian"},{"time":88913,"text":"brought up in Bengal."},{"time":91060,"text":"And two of the things about Bengal:"},{"time":93540,"text":"they like their savory dishes"},{"time":96052,"text":"and they like their sweets."},{"time":97864,"text":"So by the time I grew up,"},{"time":99635,"text":"again, I had a well-established passion for food."},{"time":103290,"text":"Now I was growing up in the late '60s and early '70s,"},{"time":106446,"text":"and there were a number of other passions I was also interested in,"},{"time":109906,"text":"but these two were the ones that differentiated me."},{"time":113223,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":114583,"text":"And then life was fine, dandy."},{"time":117434,"text":"Everything was okay,"},{"time":119092,"text":"until I got to about the age of 26,"},{"time":122971,"text":"and I went to a movie called \"Short Circuit.\""},{"time":126583,"text":"Oh, some of you have seen it."},{"time":128583,"text":"And apparently it's being remade right now"},{"time":131958,"text":"and it's going to be coming out next year."},{"time":133987,"text":"It's the story of this experimental robot"},{"time":137406,"text":"which got electrocuted and found a life."},{"time":140363,"text":"And as it ran, this thing was saying, \"Give me input. Give me input.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":144500,"text":"And I suddenly realized that for a robot"},{"time":147004,"text":"both information as well as food"},{"time":150473,"text":"were the same thing."},{"time":152667,"text":"Energy came to it in some form or shape,"},{"time":155292,"text":"data came to it in some form or shape."},{"time":157429,"text":"And I began to think,"},{"time":159875,"text":"I wonder what it would be like"},{"time":161625,"text":"to start imagining myself"},{"time":164069,"text":"as if energy and information were the two things I had as input --"},{"time":168450,"text":"as if food and information were similar in some form or shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172507,"text":"I started doing some research then, and this was the 25-year journey,"},{"time":175898,"text":"and started finding out"},{"time":177327,"text":"that actually human beings as primates"},{"time":181035,"text":"have far smaller stomachs"},{"time":183650,"text":"than should be the size for our body weight"},{"time":186884,"text":"and far larger brains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189819,"text":"And as I went to research that even further,"},{"time":193113,"text":"I got to a point where I discovered something"},{"time":196708,"text":"called the expensive tissue hypothesis."},{"time":200102,"text":"That actually for a given body mass of a primate"},{"time":204192,"text":"the metabolic rate was static."},{"time":206755,"text":"What changed was the balance of the tissues available."},{"time":210513,"text":"And two of the most expensive tissues in our human body"},{"time":214133,"text":"are nervous tissue and digestive tissue."},{"time":217902,"text":"And what transpired was that people had put forward a hypothesis"},{"time":222079,"text":"that was apparently coming up with some fabulous results by about 1995."},{"time":226584,"text":"It's a lady named Leslie Aiello."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229542,"text":"And the paper then suggested that you traded one for the other."},{"time":234334,"text":"If you wanted your brain for a particular body mass to be large,"},{"time":238042,"text":"you had to live with a smaller gut."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241189,"text":"That then set me off completely"},{"time":244023,"text":"to say, Okay, these two are connected."},{"time":246743,"text":"So I looked at the cultivation of information as if it were food"},{"time":250929,"text":"and said, So we were hunter-gathers of information."},{"time":253750,"text":"We moved from that to becoming farmers and cultivators of information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258125,"text":"Does that really explain what we're seeing"},{"time":259875,"text":"with the intellectual property battles nowadays?"},{"time":262625,"text":"Because those people who were hunter-gatherers in origin"},{"time":265958,"text":"wanted to be free and roam and pick up information as they wanted,"},{"time":269625,"text":"and those that were in the business of farming information"},{"time":272250,"text":"wanted to build fences around it,"},{"time":274625,"text":"create ownership and wealth and structure and settlement."},{"time":278296,"text":"So there was always going to be a tension within that."},{"time":281260,"text":"And everything I saw in the cultivation"},{"time":283317,"text":"said there were huge fights amongst the foodies"},{"time":285875,"text":"between the cultivators and the hunter-gatherers."},{"time":288102,"text":"And this is happening here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290417,"text":"When I moved to preparation, this same thing was true,"},{"time":293298,"text":"expect that there were two schools."},{"time":295625,"text":"One group of people said you can distill your information,"},{"time":298708,"text":"you can extract value, separate it and serve it up,"},{"time":302083,"text":"while another group turned around"},{"time":303827,"text":"and said no, no you can ferment it."},{"time":305564,"text":"You bring it all together and mash it up"},{"time":308229,"text":"and the value emerges that way."},{"time":310318,"text":"The same is again true with information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312979,"text":"But consumption was where it started getting really enjoyable."},{"time":316698,"text":"Because what I began to see then"},{"time":319055,"text":"was there were so many different ways people would consume this."},{"time":322500,"text":"They'd buy it from the shop as raw ingredients."},{"time":324988,"text":"Do you cook it? Do you have it served to you?"},{"time":327129,"text":"Do you go to a restaurant?"},{"time":328817,"text":"The same is true every time as I started thinking about information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332591,"text":"The analogies were getting crazy --"},{"time":335104,"text":"that information had sell-by dates,"},{"time":337800,"text":"that people had misused information that wasn't dated properly"},{"time":341750,"text":"and could really make an effect on the stock market,"},{"time":344083,"text":"on corporate values, etc."},{"time":346486,"text":"And by this time I was hooked."},{"time":348882,"text":"And this is about 23 years into this process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351877,"text":"And I began to start thinking of myself"},{"time":354167,"text":"as we start having mash-ups of fact and fiction,"},{"time":357638,"text":"docu-dramas, mockumentaries, whatever you call it."},{"time":361125,"text":"Are we going to reach the stage"},{"time":362585,"text":"where information has a percentage for fact associated with it?"},{"time":367143,"text":"We start labeling information for the fact percentage?"},{"time":370580,"text":"Are we going to start looking at what happens"},{"time":373208,"text":"when your information source is turned off, as a famine?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376787,"text":"Which brings me to the final element of this."},{"time":379354,"text":"Clay Shirky once stated that there is no such animal as information overload,"},{"time":382500,"text":"there is only filter failure."},{"time":385667,"text":"I put it to you that information,"},{"time":388292,"text":"if viewed from the point of food,"},{"time":390689,"text":"is never a production issue; you never speak of food overload."},{"time":394575,"text":"Fundamentally it's a consumption issue."},{"time":396771,"text":"And we have to start thinking"},{"time":398792,"text":"about how we create diets within ourselves, exercise within ourselves,"},{"time":404173,"text":"to have the faculties to be able to deal with information,"},{"time":406708,"text":"to have the labeling to be able to do it responsibly."},{"time":410458,"text":"In fact, when I saw \"Supersize Me,\" I starting thinking of saying,"},{"time":414292,"text":"What would happen"},{"time":416250,"text":"if an individual had 31 days nonstop Fox News?"},{"time":420444,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":421808,"text":"Would there be time to be able to work with it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":424710,"text":"So you start really understanding"},{"time":427673,"text":"that you can have diseases, toxins, a need to balance your diet,"},{"time":434027,"text":"and once you start looking, and from that point on,"},{"time":436938,"text":"everything I have done in terms of the consumption of information,"},{"time":440625,"text":"the production of information, the preparation of information,"},{"time":443955,"text":"I've looked at from the viewpoint of food."},{"time":447488,"text":"It has probably not helped my waistline any"},{"time":449958,"text":"because I like practicing on both sides."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452446,"text":"But I'd like to leave you with just that question:"},{"time":456167,"text":"If you began to think of all the information that you consume"},{"time":459150,"text":"the way you think of food,"},{"time":460733,"text":"what would you do differently?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462507,"text":"Thank you very much for your time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464708,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}